show.title: Divine Doctor, Protector of Beauties
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/KGanPA
show.description: A brilliant doctor with secret powers returns to city life, trying to stay out of trouble. But when beautiful women around him face danger, he can’t just walk away. Using his healing skills and hidden strength, he protects them from powerful enemies. He may not want attention, but being a hero seems to follow him everywhere.
